pageContext.description: Several holes worn in thin places on one side, through which the wood is seen. Well, but roughly made. Casting flash remains on socket. Shaft end still in socket.
pageContext.associations: A hoard containing at least 53 articles in 63 fragments, mostly swords, ferrules, spearheads, and rings.
